<div class="shogun-root" data-shogun-id="6735ae928f9dc68cdb21338b" data-shogun-site-id="a08fefdd-b4e3-4a03-a05d-ab654ccb6451" data-shogun-section-id="6735ae928f9dc68cdb21338b" data-shogun-section-version-id="6904e68b255cf1f556c5359a" data-shogun-platform-type="shopify" data-shogun-variant-id="6904e68b255cf1f556c535df" data-shogun-page-type="section" data-shogun-power-up-type="" data-shogun-power-up-id="" data-region="main"> <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://a.shgcdn2.com/css-2025-08-04-5653/6904e68b255cf1f556c5359a_6904e68b255cf1f556c535df.css"/> <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:800,normal|Poppins:700"/> <script type="text/javascript" src="https://a.shgcdn2.com/js-2025-09-16-1610/global-assets-e0a3cf438b6ce162ff2dec766d2e274cae1e8216.js" defer></script> <div id="s-0e284d05-2412-4924-9ca8-242ddd7681d0" class="shg-c shg-align-left"> <div class="shogun-heading-component"> <h2> Most Asked </h2> </div> </div> <div id="s-54fe0d84-6ae5-49c0-93e2-d22bf3c6fb4b" class="shg-c "> <div class="shogun-accordion-wrapper" data-multi=""> <div class="shogun-accordion"> <div class="shogun-accordion-heading"> <div class="shogun-accordion-header"> <h4 class="shogun-accordion-title"> How do I contact customer support? </h4> <div class="shogun-accordion-icon shogun-icon-plus"> <span/> </div> </div> </div> <div class="shogun-accordion-body"> <div id="s-ddcb7f58-82ce-4343-a6fa-40ea3e4e8102" class="shg-c "> <div class="shg-rich-text shg-theme-text-content"><p><span style="font-family: inherit; color: rgb(47, 72, 76);" data-fontfamily="(Default)"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Need assistance? Reach out to our customer support team via email at <span style="color: rgb(40, 180, 115);"><a style="color: rgb(40, 180, 115);" href="mailto:orders@xx-xyathletics.com">orders@xx-xyathletics.com</a></span>. We'll do our best to get back to you within one business day.</span></span></p></div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="shogun-accordion"> <div class="shogun-accordion-heading"> <div class="shogun-accordion-header"> <h4 class="shogun-accordion-title"> How do make a return or exchange? </h4> <div class="shogun-accordion-icon shogun-icon-plus"> <span/> </div> </div> </div> <div class="shogun-accordion-body"> <div id="s-c40a05fe-4f44-41c5-a67e-034d9ff9deeb" class="shg-c "> <div class="shg-rich-text shg-theme-text-content"><h5><span style="font-weight: bold;" data-fontweight="700"><strong>U.S Return &amp; Exchange Policy</strong></span></h5> <p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(47, 72, 76);" data-fontfamily="(Default)" data-fontweight="Normal"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Not completely satisfied with your purchase? We&rsquo;ve got you covered! Returns and exchanges are accepted within 45 days. Your first return or exchange from an order is <strong>free</strong> for U.S. shipments. Additional returns or exchanges from the same order may incur shipping fees.</span></span></p> <p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(47, 72, 76);" data-fontfamily="(Default)" data-fontweight="Normal"><span style="font-size: 16px;">To qualify for a refund, all returned items must be in their original condition&mdash;unused, unwashed, and ready to be re-loved. That means no stains or markings, including deodorant! If we find signs of wear, odors, or damage, your refund may be adjusted accordingly. Let&rsquo;s keep it fresh and fair!</span></span></p> <p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(47, 72, 76);" data-fontfamily="(Default)" data-fontweight="Normal"><span style="font-size: 16px;"> Visit our <span style="color: rgb(45, 194, 107);"><a style="color: rgb(45, 194, 107);" href="https://www.xx-xyathletics.com/a/service?" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">returns portal</a></span> for all the details on how to return or exchange your order.</span></span></p> <h5><strong>International Return &amp; Exchange Policy </strong></h5> <p>At this time, we <strong>do not offer returns or exchanges for international orders</strong>.</p> <p>If you have any questions or concerns about your order, please reach out to us at <span style="font-family: inherit; color: rgb(47, 72, 76);" data-fontfamily="(Default)"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: rgb(40, 180, 115);"><a style="color: rgb(40, 180, 115);" href="mailto:orders@xx-xyathletics.com">orders@xx-xyathletics.com</a></span></span></span> and our team will be happy to help.</p></div> </div> <div id="s-3ca8f41a-0a4a-4a4e-9a9a-089e6c3cf82a-root" class="shg-c shg-btn-wrapper shg-align-center"> <a id="s-3ca8f41a-0a4a-4a4e-9a9a-089e6c3cf82a" class="shg-btn shg-cse shg-btn-text " href="https://www.xx-xyathletics.com/a/service?"> START A RETURN </a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="shogun-accordion"> <div class="shogun-accordion-heading"> <div class="shogun-accordion-header"> <h4 class="shogun-accordion-title"> Can I return or exchange a final sale item? </h4> <div class="shogun-accordion-icon shogun-icon-plus"> <span/> </div> </div> </div> <div class="shogun-accordion-body"> <div id="s-9c1feca6-deca-40c9-891e-c428d8e5c9df" class="shg-c "> <div class="shg-rich-text shg-theme-text-content"><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(47, 72, 76);" data-fontfamily="(Default)" data-fontweight="Normal"><span style="font-size: 16px;">All final sale items are non-returnable and non-exchangeable once purchased. Please double-check your size and details before completing your order.</span></span></p></div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="shogun-accordion"> <div class="shogun-accordion-heading"> <div class="shogun-accordion-header"> <h4 class="shogun-accordion-title"> Can I update or cancel my order after it's been placed? </h4> <div class="shogun-accordion-icon shogun-icon-plus"> <span/> </div> </div> </div> <div class="shogun-accordion-body"> <div id="s-31497b7c-6635-4265-b163-d30a8a0127cb" class="shg-c "> <div class="shg-rich-text shg-theme-text-content"><p>We have a wonderful but small team, who are highly dedicated to our mission and providing the best experience we can while shopping with us. We will certainly do our best if we can to update your order, but may not be able too if it is processing. We appreciate your support.</p></div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="shogun-accordion"> <div class="shogun-accordion-heading"> <div class="shogun-accordion-header"> <h4 class="shogun-accordion-title"> Can I apply a discount code after my order has been placed? </h4> <div class="shogun-accordion-icon shogun-icon-plus"> <span/> </div> </div> </div> <div class="shogun-accordion-body"> <div id="s-c52541fc-6a16-4983-a01b-cccb0e8e09ea" class="shg-c "> <div class="shg-rich-text shg-theme-text-content"><p>Once your order is placed, we&rsquo;re unable to apply discount codes. Make sure to enter your code before checking out to enjoy the savings!</p></div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="shogun-accordion"> <div class="shogun-accordion-heading"> <div class="shogun-accordion-header"> <h4 class="shogun-accordion-title"> How can I make a donation? </h4> <div class="shogun-accordion-icon shogun-icon-plus"> <span/> </div> </div> </div> <div class="shogun-accordion-body"> <div id="s-035f7a91-a76d-46f1-8751-25b5520cb6a3" class="shg-c "> <div class="shg-rich-text shg-theme-text-content"><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(47, 72, 76);" data-fontfamily="(Default)" data-fontweight="Normal"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Thank you for standing with us in the fight to save women&rsquo;s sports! Your support fuels our mission. To make a donation and join the movement, head over to <a href="https://www.xx-xyathletics.org/">our donation page</a>.</span></span></p></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>
